<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Life on SXYAZI</title><link>https://sxyz.blog/tags/life/</link><description>Recent content in Life on SXYAZI</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 11 Aug 2018 23:04:11 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://sxyz.blog/tags/life/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>选择现在，还是选择未来？</title><link>https://sxyz.blog/posts/life/present-and-future/</link><pubDate>Sat, 11 Aug 2018 23:04:11 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://sxyz.blog/posts/life/present-and-future/</guid><description>只有明确方向，才会知晓要前进的道路。而这个方向，有人选择向前迸发，有人迫于形势向后倒退，还有人选择止步不前。对于现实与未来的选择，也是如此。如果现实与未来只能选择它们一个，你又会怎么选择？ 事例 有人可能</description></item></channel></rss>